extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.WindowListener, java.awt.event.ActionListener, javax.swing.event.ChangeListener, com.apple.eawt.OpenFilesHandler
    This is the main class for the application, and contains the main method entry point. It also contains various listeners for shutdowns, and an important list of database connections
